    "删除 plist 仅移除自动执行配置，不影响应用本身。删除后该任务不再自动运行（如开机自启或定时执行）。系统级操作需要管理员密码授权。" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Deleting a plist only removes the automatic execution schedule — it does not affect the app itself. The task will no longer run automatically. System-level operations require administrator password."
          }
        }
      }
    },
